-- China appoints ICBC as yuan clearing bank in Luxembourg
-- By China economics team
-- Tue Sep 16, 2014 04:16AM EDT
-- None



BEIJING, Sept 16 (Reuters) - China's central bank said on Tuesday it had appointed Industrial and Commercial Bank of China <1398.HK> <601398.SS>, the country's largest bank, as the yuan clearing service bank in Luxembourg - the latest move to expand the offshore yuan market.

